### Greeter — helloworld example
### Compatible with VS Code REST Client and JetBrains HTTP Client.

@host = http://localhost:8000

### 1. Say hello (no DB)
GET {{host}}/helloworld/world

### 2. Create a greeter row (writes to Postgres via ent)
# @name create
GET {{host}}/greeter/create/hi-from-rest-client

### 3. Fetch the greeter we just created
GET {{host}}/greeter/{{create.response.body.id}}

### 4. Fetch a specific greeter by id (paste manually)
@id = 1
GET {{host}}/greeter/{{id}}
